Line (Voltage) Monitoring Software
==================================

This directory contains a collection of software for interfacing with a
TekPower TP4000ZC digital multi-meter (DMM) for monitoring AC line voltage.

This software depends on the following python modules:
  * tp4000zc.py (from https://github.com/Xuth/tp4000_dmm)
  * pySerial
  * pytz
  * wxPython

Contents
--------
tp4000zc.py
  Python module for interfacing with the DMM and reading data.

lineMonitor.py
  Python script for logging line voltages.
